# Agent automations

At **session start** (before prioritizing work or claiming shipped/fixed):

```bash
node tools/agent-session-start.js
```

Add `--full` before ship claims (includes hermes-mobile Jest CI).

**Hermes Mobile:** session start prints continuous E2E status from `latest.json`. After edits under `hermes-mobile/`, agents kickstart `com.igor.hermes-mobile-continuous-e2e` — see [hermes-mobile/AGENTS.md](../../hermes-mobile/AGENTS.md). Never ask the user to run Maestro or reload the app manually.

If LaunchAgents are missing, install once:

```bash
bash scripts/install-agent-launchagents.sh
./install.sh
```

Catalog: [docs/CURSOR-AUTOMATIONS.md](../../docs/CURSOR-AUTOMATIONS.md). Decision stack: [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md).
